Ma Asia Hema , kaulana loa ka uala. Ma Inia, ʻo nā kīʻaha ʻuala kaulana loa ʻo aloo ki sabzi , batata vada , a me samosa , ʻo ia ka ʻuala mashed spicy i hui pū ʻia me kahi mea ʻai liʻiliʻi i hoʻopiha ʻia i loko o ka palaoa conical, a hoʻomoʻi hohonu. ʻO ka ʻuala kekahi mea nui e like me nā meaʻai wikiwiki, e like me ka aloo chaat, kahi i kālua ʻia a lawelawe ʻia me ka chutney . Ma ka ʻĀina ʻĀkau, ʻo ka alu dum a me ka alu paratha kahi mea punahele o ka meaʻai; ʻO ka mua he ʻuala ʻuala, ʻo ka lua, he ʻano chapati paʻa.

ʻO kahi kīʻaha i kapa ʻia ʻo masala dosa mai South India he mea kaulana loa ma India a pau. He pancake lahilahi ia o ka laiki a me ka paila pulupulu i ʻōwili ʻia ma luna o ka ʻuala ʻala a ʻai ʻia me ka sambhar a me ka chutney. ʻO Poori ma ke kūkulu hema ʻo India, ʻo ia hoʻi ma Tamil Nadu, ʻaneʻane lawe ʻia me ka masal ʻuala. ʻO nā meaʻai punahele ʻē aʻe he alu tikki a me nā mea pakoda.

ʻO Vada pav kahi kīʻaha meaʻai wikiwiki loa ma Mumbai a me nā wahi ʻē aʻe ma Maharashtra ma India.

Ua kaulana loa ʻo Aloo posto (he curry me nā ʻuala a me nā ʻanoʻano poppy) ma East India, ʻo ia hoʻi ʻo Bengal. ʻOiai ʻaʻole maoli ka ʻuala i India, ua lilo ia i ʻāpana koʻikoʻi o ka meaʻai ma ka ʻāina a ʻoi aku ka hoʻomākaukau ʻana i nā meaʻai ʻĀkau. Ma Tamil Nadu ua loaʻa i kēia ʻuʻu kahi inoa e pili ana i kona ʻano 'urulai-k-kizhangu' (உருளைக் கிழங்கு) ʻo ia hoʻi ka ʻuala cylindrical.

ʻO ka Aloo gosht , ʻuala a me ka ʻiʻo curry , ʻo ia kekahi o nā meaʻai kaulana ma Asia Hema , ʻoi aku hoʻi ma Pakistan .